sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Buyer as Buyer
    participant FE_B as Buyer React UI
    participant SocketIO as Socket.IO Server
    participant DB as PostgreSQL Database
    participant FE_S as Seller React UI
    actor Seller as Seller

    Note over Buyer, Seller: WebSocket Connection Setup
    Buyer->>FE_B: Open Chat Window with Seller
    FE_B->>SocketIO: connect (with JWT auth token)
    SocketIO->>SocketIO: Validate token & Map userId to socketId
    Seller->>FE_S: Open Chat Window with Buyer
    FE_S->>SocketIO: connect (with JWT auth token)
    SocketIO->>SocketIO: Validate token & Map userId to socketId

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Buyer, SocketIO: Sending a Message
        Buyer->>FE_B: Type message & click "Send"
        FE_B->>SocketIO: emit "send_message" {receiverId, message, attachment}
        SocketIO->>DB: INSERT INTO direct_messages (sender_id, receiver_id, message, is_read)
        DB-->>SocketIO: Message saved (id, created_at)
        
        alt Recipient is Online
            SocketIO->>FE_S: emit "receive_message" {id, sender_id, message, created_at}
            FE_S->>SocketIO: emit "message_read" {messageId}
            SocketIO->>DB: UPDATE direct_messages SET is_read = true WHERE id = messageId
            SocketIO->>FE_B: emit "message_read_receipt" {messageId}
            FE_B-->>Buyer: Show double tick (Read)
            FE_S-->>Seller: Render message in chat bubbles
        else Recipient is Offline
            SocketIO->>DB: Keep is_read = false
            SocketIO->>DB: INSERT INTO notifications (user_id, type, title, body)
            SocketIO-->>FE_B: Message sent (Single tick)
            FE_B-->>Buyer: Show single tick (Sent)
        end
    end
